  "bodyHtml": "<h1>今日原油市场每日监测报告 (2026-07-03)</h1>\n<h2>核心摘要</h2>\n<p>今日原油价格小幅收涨，主要受到美国独立日假期前补库需求的支撑。布伦特原油（Brent）收报每桶 71.80 美元，日内上涨 0.32%[来源：Trading Economics]；WTI原油收报每桶 68.69 美元，日内上涨 0.16%[来源：Vietnam.vn]。尽管收盘上涨，但盘中价格曾一度触及自2月下旬中东冲突爆发以来的最低水平，主要由于市场对供给增加和霍尔木兹海峡局势不确定性的担忧情绪交织。</p>\n<h2>1. 价格走势</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指标</th>\n<th>收盘价 (USD/bbl)</th>\n<th>日变动 %</th>\n<th>来源</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Brent Crude (布伦特原油)</td>\n<td>71.80</td>\n<td>+0.32%</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGQGwtJX4yZTImea6CCYoQ1sVyy57P413t2jQfEIyGjg61OM0OlnfLzQXOVzLsV3aQWoSA14Sn6OKpid4f02EKaZgI_0ffQJQC0pehO4KKDVZtHedqOwc1Lbnojn1dG0yN-tV_caQDEwpjcq_E=\">Trading Economics</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFVtrIFxXIVSb8MGCCm2apzIdOboVzZHxlq-g5LctS3MBvarFDJFOOALRs9k0Ga2C7GKt375xZ5S8sJENqHyAg3l96ZlyMSSs35WVc1B_Uq1l5socbA6k1wL8zt8bcxAMyYAJkmo27BWS2fV1oyAXxt5cJZolTJdsKrII45yoDlwTMb4cHOeSiyQUA0ISTY2iLG02iRr0EOnzmVE8_M6EYS8ZP-OUCDW5lMTELQlhxMx0KBiTOu_HFH5w==\">Morningstar</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE-ihGaE0nf91XIPBeCqkOPga5Dh3iVd5tTuyzcLfzem_JB6vEc8IVisdSif4i15Z7jI7Z3cnXhVy2ffYprp1DT9mQYqkqnXPLPRrYhjR9zUW_OUxPk4zjnqnnCBRHr2y_sGTdlSlo2oe8ObrIMXAz-AvrtJVLyBjduL_qz0sHqvvJAFwVNtlfiZP5sFAAz\">Rigzone</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>WTI Crude (WTI原油)</td>\n<td>68.69</td>\n<td>+0.16%</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFRPvIjDTo6cTsZixxtDeb1j9LzjsdSJeY9uRKbXKbIdo_818M8Gz6X_m14et4n5yGiQkvFIfUbtXXTF0Vqpbi3X1cgPMLSoLLH3MbtYWdsK9rwcnh5NHnW1zvfuzzHJlFrnRwlFYRQzr_WJ2iwUmQ8H_jjR1ZCV61Afmy7sjr4rZdPqExmoZxK\">Vietnam.vn</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFVtrIFxXIVSb8MGCCm2apzIdOboVzZHxlq-g5LctS3MBvarFDJFOOALRs9k0Ga2C7GKt375xZ5S8sJENqHyAg3l96ZlyMSSs35WVc1B_Uq1l5socbA6k1wL8zt8bcxAMyYAJkmo27BWS2fV1oyAXxt5cJZolTJdsKrII45yoDlwTMb4cHOeSiyQUA0ISTY2iLG02iRr0EOnzmVE8_M6EYS8ZP-OUCDW5lMTELQlhxMx0KBiTOu_HFH5w==\">Morningstar</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>2. OPEC+ 与供给侧动态</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>配额上调与政策信号</strong>：OPEC+七个核心成员国（沙特阿拉伯、俄罗斯、伊拉克、科威特、哈萨克斯坦、阿尔及利亚和阿曼）在2026年6月7日的会议上决定，将7月份的集体原油生产配额上调18.8万桶/日，使7月份的总产量目标达到约3583万桶/日<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFye6qw_reBB5IFuZDiJ5w0Rq_RkEGusnO_oB3MLEt3vcemedXFUcz8VQvV8zxEafBSiAOJQhjeSdMFl5rkoRz_vzEIUCOIovwqRs667JKACETOvi2UlQpnS95VCzZokjH0jW1m1v44pq0=\">来源：OPEC</a>。这标志着自2026年4月以来连续第四个月逐步撤回自2023年4月开始的自愿减产措施<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGRf3gLBrCf7S8HaXvUQuzm4-xVelANlWsiZoCeYu6vWeagu3uxO4tlO1EgqjCdJycELzvCqYTbHLgGfKxqrwqHXtbrq1Z4FWIkgh91udqq2xUe0J41AJ8f6GUYtvrXQjc3PHMT0IiJKQqoVmIbbFm9s17MieOD4kGabk3DsA4yNchEVjwOYnmDtIazCxyOvDvcWcMUPjpunG5qIoTayfXhbuT_uifjsHgJLCyyxmE=\">来源：Argus Media</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>成员国变动影响</strong>：由于阿拉伯联合酋长国（UAE）自2026年5月1日起正式退出OPEC和OPEC+联盟，导致此前的增产幅度计划由原先的20.6万桶/日修正为了18.8万桶/日<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGRf3gLBrCf7S8HaXvUQuzm4-xVelANlWsiZoCeYu6vWeagu3uxO4tlO1EgqjCdJycELzvCqYTbHLgGfKxqrwqHXtbrq1Z4FWIkgh91udqq2xUe0J41AJ8f6GUYtvrXQjc3PHMT0IiJKQqoVmIbbFm9s17MieOD4kGabk3DsA4yNchEVjwOYnmDtIazCxyOvDvcWcMUPjpunG5qIoTayfXhbuT_uifjsHgJLCyyxmE=\">来源：Argus Media</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>霍尔木兹海峡局势持续紧张</strong>：自2026年2月下旬冲突爆发以来，霍尔木兹海峡维持高度紧张，目前航行量仍比正常水平低约70%<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEaou0WtxFxNs997bF2RYXs7cjSSkStjSDCmLYVbJx1lTR1lTqt4KC0aDqQbPbTcXNPj30iOF8bYvGS4tR8cmuUlX0Ste8TgaElw4yb09zEM4WFApdZ\">来源：Hormuz Strait Monitor</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFQ3m34f65UJQL_8Hw2YYjc3Ia0gYHoLevcEbD6uYJZXCOPK6HcwRteObBIGt_Mx3F6CcigWILyKlUU7x202RrafOXrftPWl8N3S-AThzQWLJQbBI5rv_Wl502ZMQ==\">PNA</a>。尽管6月中旬签署了临时备忘录，但7月2日伊朗军方发出“强硬回应”警告，要求所有油轮必须使用德黑兰批准的路线<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFop5dXaqPh2S_vmi6ExPo5sGb0D6w-bBu9F4Q2FTtK7s3OuQJkgJ9ILg532U0-GFmjdBnC-GhFu-ykh_v6peVnMLTx0cU6-Bqygmroh13csjf5Gd_1DwTotDYDrIXH6UuRsIOMFklviYJEtu4WTGfiuLOm1IHQfVk8USpHnCbBPO2eJ3wjSqVFfrfHl2nzYyH_aQQzvSr-dHXoXjMQSGIKyj7neaqxIn5d2glYan8jHJBwS20QSCFikZDoE2qSz2VmMv0cBWQP5NRmSCff0TXSKNJe\">来源：The Hindu</a>。这使得OPEC+的增配额多属于“纸面产量”，难以完全转化为中东国家的实际物理出口<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEr-Q78xT4HhhWO2ftXtbNRJfXLXy6JirR8yFCoei7JANiVxGdLVIeTizcW58MG1yfHV4UpfuJ0V4-60aJ7xBgpiXBH4WdKBn6vmfBAYt2dYSdQCHx1ge9476VGQqvFbANbysijRirg6m3iP52Cxli-lU6kscEWaynrAZYvDhNOjtkSOR4HBaVeQCROKcvjAA==\">来源：Oil &amp; Gas Middle East</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. 库存与需求</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>EIA库存数据（截至2026年6月26日当周，于7月1日发布）</strong></li>\n<li><strong>商业库存减少</strong>：美国商业原油库存（不含战略石油储备SPR）减少 380 万桶（即 3800 kb），总库存降至 4.084 亿桶（即 408,400 kb）<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2N_bq_-WO9ccGfd-FTdq_pAtMeJhIkYIiv1vryUyuiGP-v5-hHd70YMDf_qspLdqrhc2xOEXB7iK-T6t1pp43ZJINtIPowAhEyE4slN1urvMbNzdQp21X4Rcl5Q==\">来源：EIA</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>精炼厂开工率回升</strong>：美国精炼厂开工率由前一周的 96.1% 上升至 96.6%，原油加工量平均达 1720 万桶/日<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG0Y2ilF5_dLVSgYLR2WC1t1CU0aSHkrUH8OA31qt7AEys-PUBPWqMbJPhF65xck-c-Zk-yf7iTSYKAqLc9WCS23K1YeMElcqkL7NRx1BI71UWJvGzw6MJjXG5V-RbllBamHNHFKXPZMngQ7GIC0JrpYC-y\">来源：EIA</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>本土产量平稳</strong>：美国原油估算产量维持在 1380 万桶/日（即 13,800 kbpd），与前一周基本持平<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG0Y2ilF5_dLVSgYLR2WC1t1CU0aSHkrUH8OA31qt7AEys-PUBPWqMbJPhF65xck-c-Zk-yf7iTSYKAqLc9WCS23K1YeMElcqkL7NRx1BI71UWJvGzw6MJjXG5V-RbllBamHNHFKXPZMngQ7GIC0JrpYC-y\">来源：EIA</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>假期前需求支撑</strong>：由于美国7月4日独立日小长假临近，燃油需求表现稳健，投资者在假期前进行了空头回补和采购，为昨日油价提供了日内的下行支撑<a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGQGwtJX4yZTImea6CCYoQ1sVyy57P413t2jQfEIyGjg61OM0OlnfLzQXOVzLsV3aQWoSA14Sn6OKpid4f02EKaZgI_0ffQJQC0pehO4KKDVZtHedqOwc1Lbnojn1dG0yN-tV_caQDEwpjcq_E=\">来源：Trading Economics</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4. 结论与后续关注</h2>\n<h3>核心判断</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>地缘溢价未退，但实际物流瓶颈限制出口</strong>：霍尔木兹海峡的限制状态使地缘政治风险溢价维持在油价中，但也同样限制了中东产油国增加出口的物理能力。</li>\n<li><strong>基本面短期偏紧</strong>：EIA库存下降 380 万桶以及炼厂利用率回升至 96.6% 均显示出当前美国夏季传统出行旺季的需求支撑。</li>\n<li><strong>宏观与微观博弈</strong>：尽管OPEC+连续四个月上调生产配额，但中东地缘冲突与阿联酋退出导致的配额基数下修令全球供需缺口仍具弹性。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>观察点</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>霍尔木兹海峡博弈</strong>：密切关注60天临时通航期后（预计8月中旬）伊朗是否强制征收通行费以及各方的外交与军事动作。</li>\n<li><strong>OPEC+实际产量监控</strong>：评估各成员国（尤其是伊拉克和哈萨克斯坦）的超额补偿性减产执行情况，而非仅仅关注账面配额的上涨。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>数据发现</h2>\n<p>由于本次内部数据API未返回有效记录（HTTP 404），以下关键字段已通过Web Search抓取填补，供数据科学家审查录入目录\n- <code>brent_close_usd</code>: 71.80 USD/bbl\n- <code>wti_close_usd</code>: 68.69 USD/bbl\n- <code>brent_change_pct</code>: +0.32%\n- <code>wti_change_pct</code>: +0.16%\n- <code>opec_target_kbpd</code>: 35,830 kbpd\n- <code>eia_inventory_change_kb</code>: -3,800 kb\n- <code>eia_total_inventory_kb</code>: 408,400 kb\n- <code>us_production_kbpd</code>: 13,800 kbpd\n- <code>refinery_utilization_pct</code>: 96.6%</p>\n<h2>数据来源</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>数据源校验 </strong>: 无（无2026-07-03日数据，错误代码 404）</li>\n<li><strong>Web Search</strong>\n  1. Brent &amp; WTI 价格与日内动态: <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGQGwtJX4yZTImea6CCYoQ1sVyy57P413t2jQfEIyGjg61OM0OlnfLzQXOVzLsV3aQWoSA14Sn6OKpid4f02EKaZgI_0ffQJQC0pehO4KKDVZtHedqOwc1Lbnojn1dG0yN-tV_caQDEwpjcq_E=\">Trading Economics</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFVtrIFxXIVSb8MGCCm2apzIdOboVzZHxlq-g5LctS3MBvarFDJFOOALRs9k0Ga2C7GKt375xZ5S8sJENqHyAg3l96ZlyMSSs35WVc1B_Uq1l5socbA6k1wL8zt8bcxAMyYAJkmo27BWS2fV1oyAXxt5cJZolTJdsKrII45yoDlwTMb4cHOeSiyQUA0ISTY2iLG02iRr0EOnzmVE8_M6EYS8ZP-OUCDW5lMTELQlhxMx0KBiTOu_HFH5w==\">Morningstar</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFRPvIjDTo6cTsZixxtDeb1j9LzjsdSJeY9uRKbXKbIdo_818M8Gz6X_m14et4n5yGiQkvFIfUbtXXTF0Vqpbi3X1cgPMLSoLLH3MbtYWdsK9rwcnh5NHnW1zvfuzzHJlFrnRwlFYRQzr_WJ2iwUmQ8H_jjR1ZCV61Afmy7sjr4rZdPqExmoZxK\">Vietnam.vn</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE-ihGaE0nf91XIPBeCqkOPga5Dh3iVd5tTuyzcLfzem_JB6vEc8IVisdSif4i15Z7jI7Z3cnXhVy2ffYprp1DT9mQYqkqnXPLPRrYhjR9zUW_OUxPk4zjnqnnCBRHr2y_sGTdlSlo2oe8ObrIMXAz-AvrtJVLyBjduL_qz0sHqvvJAFwVNtlfiZP5sFAAz\">Rigzone</a>\n  2. OPEC 产量配额与阿联酋退出: <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFye6qw_reBB5IFuZDiJ5w0Rq_RkEGusnO_oB3MLEt3vcemedXFUcz8VQvV8zxEafBSiAOJQhjeSdMFl5rkoRz_vzEIUCOIovwqRs667JKACETOvi2UlQpnS95VCzZokjH0jW1m1v44pq0=\">OPEC.org</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGRf3gLBrCf7S8HaXvUQuzm4-xVelANlWsiZoCeYu6vWeagu3uxO4tlO1EgqjCdJycELzvCqYTbHLgGfKxqrwqHXtbrq1Z4FWIkgh91udqq2xUe0J41AJ8f6GUYtvrXQjc3PHMT0IiJKQqoVmIbbFm9s17MieOD4kGabk3DsA4yNchEVjwOYnmDtIazCxyOvDvcWcMUPjpunG5qIoTayfXhbuT_uifjsHgJLCyyxmE=\">Argus Media</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEr-Q78xT4HhhWO2ftXtbNRJfXLXy6JirR8yFCoei7JANiVxGdLVIeTizcW58MG1yfHV4UpfuJ0V4-60aJ7xBgpiXBH4WdKBn6vmfBAYt2dYSdQCHx1ge9476VGQqvFbANbysijRirg6m3iP52Cxli-lU6kscEWaynrAZYvDhNOjtkSOR4HBaVeQCROKcvjAA==\">Oil &amp; Gas Middle East</a>\n  3. 霍尔木兹海峡通航与地缘局势: <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEaou0WtxFxNs997bF2RYXs7cjSSkStjSDCmLYVbJx1lTR1lTqt4KC0aDqQbPbTcXNPj30iOF8bYvGS4tR8cmuUlX0Ste8TgaElw4yb09zEM4WFApdZ\">Hormuz Strait Monitor</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFQ3m34f65UJQL_8Hw2YYjc3Ia0gYHoLevcEbD6uYJZXCOPK6HcwRteObBIGt_Mx3F6CcigWILyKlUU7x202RrafOXrftPWl8N3S-AThzQWLJQbBI5rv_Wl502ZMQ==\">PNA</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFop5dXaqPh2S_vmi6ExPo5sGb0D6w-bBu9F4Q2FTtK7s3OuQJkgJ9ILg532U0-GFmjdBnC-GhFu-ykh_v6peVnMLTx0cU6-Bqygmroh13csjf5Gd_1DwTotDYDrIXH6UuRsIOMFklviYJEtu4WTGfiuLOm1IHQfVk8USpHnCbBPO2eJ3wjSqVFfrfHl2nzYyH_aQQzvSr-dHXoXjMQSGIKyj7neaqxIn5d2glYan8jHJBwS20QSCFikZDoE2qSz2VmMv0cBWQP5NRmSCff0TXSKNJe\">The Hindu</a>\n  4. EIA每周库存数据: <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2N_bq_-WO9ccGfd-FTdq_pAtMeJhIkYIiv1vryUyuiGP-v5-hHd70YMDf_qspLdqrhc2xOEXB7iK-T6t1pp43ZJINtIPowAhEyE4slN1urvMbNzdQp21X4Rcl5Q==\">EIA.gov</a> / <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG0Y2ilF5_dLVSgYLR2WC1t1CU0aSHkrUH8OA31qt7AEys-PUBPWqMbJPhF65xck-c-Zk-yf7iTSYKAqLc9WCS23K1YeMElcqkL7NRx1BI71UWJvGzw6MJjXG5V-RbllBamHNHFKXPZMngQ7GIC0JrpYC-y\">EIA Weekly Status</a></li>\n</ul>"
}
